\[\delta 
\equiv \frac{\alpha}{\Delta \theta} 
= \frac{eB \lambda_B}{m_e c^2} 
\underbrace{=}_{(1)} \frac{\gamma \lambda_B}{r_L} 
\simeq \frac{\gamma }{k_B r_L}\tag{4}\]

<p>(4)å¼ã®é€”ä¸­å¼ã‹ã‚‰ã‚ã‹ã‚‹ã‚ˆã†ã«ã€\(\delta\)ã¯\(B, \lambda_B\)ã«ã—ã‹ä¾å­˜ã—ã¾ã›ã‚“ã€‚
ã¾ãŸã•ã‚‰ã«æ‰±ã„ã‚„ã™ã„ã‚ˆã†ã«ã€æœ€å¾Œã®å¤‰å½¢ã§ã¯\(\lambda_B \simeq k_B^{-1}\)ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«æ³¢æ•°ã‚’ç”¨ã„ã¦è¡¨ç¾ã‚’ã—ã¾ã—ãŸã€‚<br />
ã•ã¦ã€ã“ã“ã‹ã‚‰ã¯å…·ä½“çš„ã«ã‚¹ãƒšã‚¯ãƒˆãƒ«ã‚’æ±‚ã‚ã‚‹å•é¡Œè¨­å®šã‚’è€ƒãˆã¦ã„ãã¾ã—ã‚‡ã†ã€‚
è»Œé“ã®ã‚ºãƒ¬ãŒéå¸¸ã«å°ã•ã„å ´åˆã€è¦³æ¸¬è€…ã¯æ”¾å°„ã‚³ãƒ¼ãƒ³ã‚’å¸¸ã«è¦‹ç¶šã‘ã‚‹ã“ã¨ã«ãªã‚Šã¾ã™ã€‚
ã“ã‚Œã«ã‚ˆã‚Šã€ã‚·ãƒ³ã‚¯ãƒ­ãƒˆãƒ­ãƒ³æ”¾å°„ã¨ã¯é•ã£ãŸã‚¹ãƒšã‚¯ãƒˆãƒ«ãŒè¦³æ¸¬ã•ã‚Œã‚‹ã¯ãšã§ã™ã€‚</p>

<p><img src="/assets/images/astroelec/jitter_01.png" alt="" /></p>

<p>ã“ã®è­°è«–ã‹ã‚‰ã€ä»Šå›æ‰±ã†å•é¡Œã¯\(\delta \ll 1\)ã®ã‚ˆã†ãªçŠ¶æ³ã§ã‚ã‚‹ã¨ã‚ã‹ã‚Šã¾ã™ã€‚
ã“ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«ã€Œç´°ã‹ãæŒ¯å‹•ã™ã‚‹(jittering)ã‚ˆã†ãªè»Œé“ã‹ã‚‰ã®æ”¾å°„ã€ã¨ã„ã†æ„å‘³ã‚’ã“ã‚ã¦ã€ã“ã‚Œã‚’ã‚¸ãƒƒã‚¿ãƒ¼æ”¾å°„(jitter radiation)ã¨å‘¼ã³ã¾ã™ã€‚</p>

<h2 id="ã‚¹ãƒšã‚¯ãƒˆãƒ«å°å‡º">ã‚¹ãƒšã‚¯ãƒˆãƒ«å°å‡º</h2>

<p>ãã‚Œã§ã¯ã‚¹ãƒšã‚¯ãƒˆãƒ«ã‚’å°å‡ºã—ã¦ã„ãã¾ã—ã‚‡ã†ã€‚
è¶…ç›¸å¯¾è«–çš„é›»å­ãŒå‡ºã™æ”¾å°„ã®é›»å ´ã¯ã€<a href="/astroelec/rad_fourier">è¼»å°„å ´ã®ãƒ•ãƒ¼ãƒªã‚¨ã‚¹ãƒšã‚¯ãƒˆãƒ«</a>ã‚ˆã‚Š</p>

\[\hat{\mathbf{E}}(\mathbf{r}, \omega) 
= \frac{-e}{2\pi c^2 R} e^{i\omega \frac{\mathbf{n} \cdot \mathbf{r}}{c}} \frac{\mathbf{n} \times \{(\mathbf{n} - \boldsymbol{\beta}) \times \hat{\mathbf{a}}_{\omega'}\}}{\kappa^2} \tag{5}\]

<p>ã§ã™ã€‚
ã“ã“ã§\(\kappa = 1 -\mathbf{n} \cdot \boldsymbol{\beta}, \hat{\mathbf{a}}_{\omega'} = \int_{-\infty}^\infty \mathbf{a} e^{i\omega' t} dt\)ã§ã™ã€‚
ã¾ãŸ\(\omega' = \omega (1-\frac{\mathbf{r}_0 \cdot \mathbf{n}}{ct'})\)ã§ã™ãŒã€ä»¥é™ã§ã¯é›»å­ã®é‹å‹•ã¯ç­‰é€Ÿç›´ç·šé‹å‹•ã§ã‚ã‚‹ã¨è€ƒãˆã¦\(\omega' = \omega (1 - \frac{\mathbf{v} \cdot \mathbf{n}}{c}) = \omega \kappa\)ã§ã‚ã‚‹ã¨ã—ã¾ã™ã€‚
ã“ã‚Œã‚ˆã‚Šã€<a href="/astroelec/energy_per_solid_angle_per_freq">å˜ä½ç«‹ä½“è§’ãƒ»å˜ä½å‘¨æ³¢æ•°ã‚ãŸã‚Šã®æ”¾å°„ã‚¨ãƒãƒ«ã‚®ãƒ¼</a>ã¯</p>

\[\frac{dW}{d\omega d\Omega} 
= c R^2 \vert \hat{\mathbf{E}} (\omega) \vert^2 
= \frac{e^2}{4\pi^2 c^3} \frac{\vert \mathbf{n} \times \{(\mathbf{n} - \boldsymbol{\beta}) \times \hat{\mathbf{a}}_{\omega'}\} \vert^2 }{\kappa^4} 
= \frac{e^2}{4\pi^2 c^3} \left( \frac{\omega}{\omega'} \right)^4 \left| \mathbf{n} \times \left\{ \left( \mathbf{n} - \boldsymbol{\beta} \right) \times \hat{\mathbf{a}}_{\omega'} \right\} \right|^2 \tag{6}\]

<p>ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«ãªã‚Šã¾ã™ã€‚
ã“ã‚Œã‚’å…¨ç«‹ä½“è§’ã§ç©åˆ†ã—ã¾ã™ã€‚
è¨ˆç®—ã«ã‚ãŸã‚Šã€è¿‘ä¼¼ã‚’æ–½ã—ã¾ã—ã‚‡ã†ã€‚
\(\mathbf{n} \cdot \boldsymbol{\beta} = \frac{v}{c} \cos \theta\)ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«ã€\(\mathbf{n}\)ã¨\(\mathbf{v}\)ã®æˆã™è§’åº¦ã‚’\(\theta\)ã¨ã—ã¾ã™ã€‚
ã“ã®ã¨ã\(\theta \simeq \Delta \theta \ll 1\)ã§ååˆ†ã«å°ã•ã„ã¨ã™ã‚‹ã¨</p>

\[\begin{align}
\kappa 
&amp;= 1 - \frac{v}{c} \cos \theta 
\simeq 1 - \frac{v}{c} \left( 1 - \frac{\theta^2}{2}\right) 
\underbrace{\simeq}_{v/c \sim 1} 1 - \frac{v}{c} + \frac{\theta^2}{2} 
\simeq \frac{1}{2} \left\{ 2 \left( 1 - \frac{v}{c} \right) + \theta^2 \right\} \notag \\
&amp;\underbrace{\simeq}_{1+\frac{v}{c} \sim 2} \frac{1}{2} \left\{ \left( 1 + \frac{v}{c} \right) \left( 1 - \frac{v}{c} \right) + \theta^2 \right\} 
= \frac{1}{2} \left( 1 - \frac{v^2}{c^2} + \theta^2 \right) 
= \frac{1}{2} (\gamma^{-2} + \theta^2) \tag{7}
\end{align}\]

<p>ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«è¿‘ä¼¼ã™ã‚‹ã“ã¨ãŒã§ãã¾ã™ã€‚
ä»¥ä¸Šã‚ˆã‚Š</p>

\[\omega' 
= \omega \kappa \ \Longrightarrow \ 
d\omega' 
= \omega \theta d\theta \tag{8}\]

<p>ã‚’å¾—ã¾ã™ã€‚
ã“ã‚Œã‚’ç”¨ã„ã‚Œã°ã€å…¨ç«‹ä½“è§’ç©åˆ†ã¯\(d\Omega = \sin \theta d\theta d\phi \simeq \theta d\theta d\phi = d\phi d\omega' / \omega\)ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«å¤‰æ•°å¤‰æ›ã•ã‚Œã¾ã™ã€‚
ç©åˆ†ç¯„å›²ã¯\(\theta: 0 \rightarrow \pi\)ã‹ã‚‰\(\omega': \omega/2\gamma^2 \rightarrow \omega (\gamma^{-2} + \pi^2) / 2\)ã¨ãªã‚Šã¾ã™ãŒã€<a href="/astroelec/rel_beaming">ç›¸å¯¾è«–çš„ãƒ“ãƒ¼ãƒŸãƒ³ã‚°åŠ¹æœ</a>ã‹ã‚‰\(\theta\)ãŒå¤§ããªéƒ¨åˆ†ã§ã®å¯„ä¸ã¯ã‚¼ãƒ­ã¨ãªã‚‹ã¯ãšã§ã™ã€‚
ã—ãŸãŒã£ã¦ã€ç©åˆ†ç¯„å›²ã®ä¸Šé™ã¯ç„¡é™å¤§ã«ã—ã¦ã‚‚å·®ã—æ”¯ãˆã‚ã‚Šã¾ã›ã‚“ã€‚
ã‚ˆã£ã¦</p>

\[\begin{align}
\frac{dW}{d\omega} 
&amp;= \frac{e^2}{2\pi c^3} \int_{\omega / 2\gamma^2}^\infty \left( \frac{\omega}{\omega'} \right)^4 \left| (\mathbf{n} \cdot \hat{\mathbf{a}}_{\omega'}) \mathbf{n} - \hat{\mathbf{a}}_{\omega'} - (\mathbf{n} \cdot \hat{\mathbf{a}}_{\omega'}) \boldsymbol{\beta} + (\mathbf{n} \cdot \boldsymbol{\beta}) \hat{\mathbf{a}}_{\omega'} \right|^2 \frac{d\omega'}{\omega} \notag \\
&amp;= \frac{e^2 \omega^3}{2\pi c^3} \int_{\omega / 2\gamma^2}^\infty \frac{\vert \hat{\mathbf{a}}_{\omega'} \vert^2}{\omega'^4} \left| 1 - \mathbf{n} \cdot \boldsymbol{\beta} \right|^2 d\omega' \tag{9}
\end{align}\]

<p>ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«ãªã‚Šã¾ã™ã€‚
ã“ã“ã§è»Œé“ã¯ã»ã¼ç›´ç·šã§ã€é›»å­ã«ã‹ã‹ã‚‹åŠ é€Ÿåº¦ã¯å¸¸ã«å‚ç›´ã§ã‚ã‚‹(\(\mathbf{n} \cdot \hat{\mathbf{a}} \sim 0\))ã¨ã„ã†è¿‘ä¼¼ã‚’ç”¨ã„ã¾ã—ãŸã€‚
ã•ã‚‰ã«</p>

\[\mathbf{n} \cdot \boldsymbol{\beta} 
= \beta \cos \theta 
\simeq \beta \left( 1 - \frac{\theta^2}{2}\right) 
\underbrace{\simeq}_{(7)} \beta \left( 1 - \frac{\omega'}{\omega} + \frac{1}{2\gamma^2}\right) \tag{10}\]

<p>ã®ã‚ˆã†ãªè¿‘ä¼¼ã‚’è¡Œã„ã€ã“ã“ã«\(\beta \sim 1\)ã‚’ä»£å…¥ã™ã‚Œã°</p>

\[\left| 1 - \mathbf{n} \cdot \boldsymbol{\beta} \right|^2 
\simeq \left( -\frac{\omega'}{\omega} + \frac{1}{2\gamma^2} \right)^2 
= \frac{\omega'^2}{\omega^2} - \frac{\omega'}{\omega \gamma^2} + \frac{1}{4\gamma^4} \tag{11}\]

<p>ã¨ãªã‚Šã¾ã™ã€‚æœ€çµ‚çš„ã«</p>

\[\frac{dW}{d\omega} 
= \frac{e^2 \omega}{2\pi c^3} \int_{\omega/ 2\gamma^2}^\infty \frac{\vert \hat{\mathbf{a}}_{\omega'} \vert^2}{\omega'^2} \left( 1 - \frac{\omega}{\omega' \gamma^2} + \frac{\omega^2}{4 \omega'^2 \gamma^4}\right) d\omega' \tag{12}\]

<p>ã‚’å¾—ã¾ã™ã€‚
ç¬¬ä¸€é …ã¯é›»å­è»Œé“ã®å¾®å°ãªæŒ¯å‹•ã«ã‚ˆã‚‹ã‚‚ã®ã€ç¬¬äºŒãƒ»ç¬¬ä¸‰é …ã¯<a href="/astroelec/rel_beaming">ç›¸å¯¾è«–çš„ãƒ“ãƒ¼ãƒŸãƒ³ã‚°</a>ã¨çµ„ã¿åˆã‚ã•ã£ãŸè¼»å°„å ´ã®è§’åº¦æ§‹é€ ã«èµ·å› ã™ã‚‹è£œæ­£ã§ã™ã€‚</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>ãƒ©ãƒ³ãƒ€ã‚¦ãƒ»ãƒªãƒ•ã‚·ãƒƒãƒ„ãªã©ã®æ–‡çŒ®ã§ã¯ã€ç¬¬ä¸‰é …ã®åˆ†æ¯ãŒ2ã«ãªã‚‹...è¿‘ä¼¼ã®ä»•æ–¹ã«ãƒŸã‚¹(?_?)
